result.name: Kam Pui Restaurant

reviews.text: Average quality food, and prices are reasonable given the location.

I have been to this restaurant for over ten years. The waitress was polite in the past. Since more tourists come to Tai O, they become rude despite stable food quality. 唔憂做嘅款. It's very disappointing.
No English-speaking servers but English menu is available. Seasonal vegetable dishes are AMAZING. Seafood fried noodles, to die for. I ordered here by pointing at the photos on their original menu.

Average quality food, and prices are reasonable given the location. English menus do not include lunch set specials (which include a drink). Service is friendly, but a little slow. Air conditioners exist for warmer days. Cash only.
Nice place for breakfast and lunch!  Noodle soup and toast are delicious!

result.adr_address: 香港大澳大澳太平街130號
result.formatted_address: 香港大澳大澳太平街130號
result.name: 金培餐廳

reviews.text: 差→差→差→食物質數難食😒😰

大澳街上，一路往內走！
走到尾端，發現豪美味的「金培餐廳」

超推》大澳蝦糕炒飯
必吃》鹹魚雞粒炒飯

星洲炒米》咖哩感十足
銀芽肉絲炒麵》又軟又硬的麵口感特別

可以吃吃看喔！👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼

從台灣來玩
這間餐廳的服務員都很親切！
8人點了大澳蝦糕炒飯、咸魚雞粒炒飯、銀芽肉絲炒麵、星州炒麵，四樣東西分著吃非常飽
份量很足！味道又非常好！
仍是35年前的味道，需則轉手2次了，但現在再由始祖班底厨房主理，所以一定OK，大家支持下啦
魷魚好味，蝦醬有特色
